entry.title: yfhuang/fastq-split
entry.summary:
fastq-split

fastq-split

This project is created for dealing with paired-end reads processed by SGA preprocess and filter. The input of fastq-split is the read seqeunces in fastq format. Paired reads and unpaired reads will be output separately.
